The,Search,API,from,Open,Addresses,UK,searches,for,UK,addresses,in,an,open,data,set,The,API,uses,JSON,over,HTTP,and,supports,partial,searches,as,well,as,multiple,query,strings,e,g,by,postcode,by,town,Responses,return,all,data,matching,the,search,terms,and,include,a,persistent,URL,for,each,address,In,addition,the,addresses,use,a,format,similar,to,the,BS,standard,and,include,latitude,and,longitude,coordinates,for,the,geographic,center,of,each,address,s,postcode,See,the,project,page,for,more,information,or,to,demo,the,Search,API